posts.post_title: T206 Flanagan with double eyes/print line
posts.post_content:
A decent looking Flanagan with a double set of eyes, easier to see on his left eye. Looks like the brown/black in the face was printed twice or missed, you can see the double eyes, eyebrows are bigger and hair is up a little too. 

  Also this card has a nice stray red printing line on the right side, plus the red has a slight color shift up on the card

  Clean SC 350/30 back. Asking $100 dlvd paypal...LOWERED! (all caps for emphasis)

One last bump and lower price...$100. Unless your name is Craig, then you can have it for $90 :)

  Otherwise, tomorrow at noon it gets thrown into the safe like a ninja star and stays there
